4. Grants for the construction in the United Kingdom of ships or mobile offshore installations begun before 1st January, 1975 as follows:—


10 per cent. of any part of the contract price attributed to the year 1972;

4 per cent. of any part of the contract price attributed to the year 1973;

3 per cent. of any part of the contract price attributed to the year 1974,

but subject to any special provisions for calculating the amount of grant for a partially constructed ship or installation.

